OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,F19 hospitals in the North West are
OL,7,Ftaking part in the test roll out of a
OL,8,Fnew scheme which will give patients
OL,9,Fand families a second opinion if
OL,10,Fthey're worried about treatment.
OL,12,FMartha's Rule was introduced after the
OL,13,Fdeath of a teenager - after a failure
OL,14,Fto escalate her to intensive care.
OL,16,FIn a wider roll out, the NHS has today
OL,17,Fannounced the 143 hospital sites that
OL,18,Fwill test and roll out Martha's Rule
OL,19,Fin its first year.
