OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FConfirmation of the first sites to
OL,7,Ftest implementation of Martha's Rule
OL,8,Fis the next step in a major patient
OL,9,Fsafety initiative, following the
OL,10,Fannouncement in February of NHS
OL,11,FEngland funding for this financial
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FThe initial target was to enrol at
OL,15,Fleast 100 sites, but due to
OL,16,Fsignificant interest from frontline
OL,17,Fclinicians this has been expanded,
OL,18,Fmeaning this first phase of the
OL,19,Fprogramme will be in place at 143
OL,20,Flocations across the country by March
OL,21,F2025.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/13
