OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FEvaluation of how the system works in
OL,7,Fthese sites over the course of this
OL,8,Fyear will inform proposals for
OL,9,FMartha's Rule to be expanded further
OL,10,Facross all acute hospitals, subject to
OL,11,Ffuture government funding.
OL,13,FThe purpose of Martha's Rule is to
OL,14,Fprovide a consistent and
OL,15,Funderstandable way for patients and
OL,16,Ffamilies to seek an urgent review if
OL,17,Ftheir or their loved one's condition
OL,18,Fdeteriorates and they are concerned
OL,19,Fthis is not being responded to.
