OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FThe scheme is named after thirteen-
OL,7,Fyear-old Martha Mills, who died from
OL,8,Fsepsis having been treated at King's
OL,9,FCollege Hospital, London, in 2021, due
OL,10,Fto a failure to escalate her to
OL,11,Fintensive care, and after her family's
OL,12,Fconcerns about her deteriorating
OL,13,Fcondition were not responded to.
OL,15,FNHS England is working with Martha's
OL,16,Fparents to develop materials to
OL,17,Fadvertise and explain the initiative
OL,18,Fin hospitals across the country, to
OL,19,Fensure it is something that all
OL,20,Fpatients, staff, and their families
OL,21,Fcan recognise.
