OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FMartha's Rule is to be made up of
OL,7,Fthree components to ensure concerns
OL,8,Fabout deterioration can be swiftly
OL,9,Fresponded to.
OL,11,FFirstly, an escalation process will be
OL,12,Favailable at all the 143 sites,
OL,13,Fadvertised throughout the hospitals on
OL,14,Fposters and leaflets, enabling
OL,15,Fpatients and families to contact a
OL,16,Fcritical care outreach team that can
OL,17,Fswiftly assess a case and escalate
OL,18,Fcare if necessary.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/13
