OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FSecondly, NHS staff will also have
OL,7,Faccess to this same process if they
OL,8,Fhave concerns about a patient's
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,FFinally, alongside this, clinicians at
OL,12,Fparticipating hospitals will also
OL,13,Fformally record daily insights and
OL,14,Finformation about a patient's health
OL,15,Fdirectly from their families, ensuring
OL,16,Fany concerning changes in behaviour or
OL,17,Fcondition noticed by the people who
OL,18,Fknow the patient best are considered
OL,19,Fby staff.
