OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FExtensive campaigning by her parents
OL,7,FMerope and Paul, supported by the
OL,8,Fcross-party think tank Demos, saw
OL,9,Fwidespread support for a single system
OL,10,Fthat allows patients or their families
OL,11,Fto trigger an urgent clinical review
OL,12,Ffrom a different team in the hospital
OL,13,Fif the patient's condition is rapidly
OL,14,Fworsening and they feel they are not
OL,15,Fgetting the care they need.
OL,17,FMerope Mills and Paul Laity, Martha's
OL,18,Fparents, said: "We are pleased that
OL,19,Fthe roll-out of Martha's Rule is off
OL,20,Fto a flying start and that the need
OL,21,Ffor it has been so widely recognised.
