OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,F"It will save lives and encourage
OL,7,Fbetter, more open, communication on
OL,8,Fhospital wards, so that patients feel
OL,9,Fthey are listened to, and partners in
OL,10,Ftheir healthcare."
