OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FProfessor Sir Stephen Powis, NHS
OL,7,Fnational medical director, said:
OL,8,F"Rolling out Martha's Rule to over 143
OL,9,FNHS sites in this first phase will
OL,10,Frepresent one of the most important
OL,11,Fchanges to patient care in recent
OL,12,Fyears, and we are pleased to have seen
OL,13,Fsuch interest from hospitals right
OL,14,Facross the country, all thanks to the
OL,15,Fmoving and dedicated campaigning by
OL,16,FMartha' parents, Merope and Paul.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
