OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,F"That is why today is such an
OL,7,Fimportant milestone, with the NHS
OL,8,Foutlining the 143 sites where this
OL,9,Fmajor patient safety initiative will
OL,10,Fbe rolled out later this year,
OL,11,Fallowing staff, patients and families
OL,12,Fto immediately raise concerns and
OL,13,Fbring about an escalation in care in
OL,14,Fan easily recognisable and fast way.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
