OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,F"The inclusion of daily insights from
OL,7,Ffamilies about their loved ones'
OL,8,Fcondition within patient records is
OL,9,Falso a really significant step and
OL,10,Fwill help staff identify changes and
OL,11,Fdeterioration using insights from
OL,12,Fthose who know the patient best.
OL,14,FWhile thankfully the need for
OL,15,Fescalation of care will hopefully only
OL,16,Fbe needed in a limited number of
OL,17,Fcases, this three-step safety net has
OL,18,Fthe opportunity to truly transform
OL,19,Fpatient care and safety."
