OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,FNHS national patient safety director
OL,7,Fand senior responsible officer for
OL,8,FMartha's Rule, Dr Aidan Fowler, said:
OL,9,F"Working closely with Martha's parents
OL,10,Fand colleagues across the NHS over the
OL,11,Flast few months on this rollout, I am
OL,12,Fin no doubt this programme will
OL,13,Fdeliver clear change and it has been
OL,14,Fso encouraging to see how many
OL,15,Fhospitals have shown interest in being
OL,16,Fpart of delivering these all-important
OL,17,Fpatient safety measures this year.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
