OL,3,CNew scheme to help patients get second
OL,4,Copinion about hospital treatment
OL,6,F"With new processes that enable both
OL,7,Fpatients and staff to raise concerns
OL,8,Fif they see someone's condition
OL,9,Fworsening, and the inclusion of
OL,10,Fpatients and their loved ones'
OL,11,Finsights in medical records, these
OL,12,Fmeasures can help us better identify
OL,13,Fand manage deterioration as part of
OL,14,Fwider work, which is a key priority
OL,15,Ffor us and will no doubt lead to
OL,16,Fimprovements in the care patients
OL,17,Freceive."
